      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEAR THE DRAGON (8) is a promising dog in the frame at 37 of 90 starts including 26 wins and was in the minors again latest (30.51) over 530m at Murray Bridge. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. LONG GULLY ASH (1) was out of placings last time (20.50) at Angle Park in a Grade 4/5, finishing sixth and beaten 14 lengths. Has already won five times from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. ETHANOL UNLEADED (4) led throughout to score two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 5 length 4th at Mt Gambier (18.25). Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Should be thereabouts. OUR LAURA ROSE (2) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.",
